{"tid":2166172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：美取消與港移交逃犯及囚犯協定  影響不大","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T09:47:55.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f1f0af47cd24c83c0f1278f270603a02169ce4","tid":2166172,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊指，美國暫停對香港國際船舶的雙重課稅寬免協議，對船運業有一定打撃，相信政府會提供其他優惠協助業界。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：「船運終止雙重稅務優惠，對香港作為船運中心，打擊是有的。這是關乎船運業運作的利益問題，相信特區政府會在其他運作上、稅務優惠上會想辦法，保持香港船運上，對外界投資或外界營運吸引性。」<br />\n<br />\n至於取消雙方移交逃犯及移交囚犯的協定，湯家驊指影響不大，因為香港不信任美國的監獄制度，一早已沒有移交囚犯到美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=402470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402470&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=0d4bddb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402470&h=21ceb4ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=402470</a>"},{"pid":"f5a7802b08d29e68b9f3d68da57305a361375266","tid":2166172,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c82ecc9ec8649626b3bf3837c6d8e20764b6dd","tid":2166172,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:24:51.000Z","msg":"宜家唔至美國停引渡呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b509fa10814af15b3020681d38e5edceb5c7d57","tid":2166172,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"咩都冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6210840c582ff18c020fdb38501119a0eba85db3","tid":2166172,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020